## RULES
- ✅ Java standard library imports first
- ✅ Framework imports (Spring, Jmix) grouped together
- ✅ Project imports last (before static imports)
- ✅ Static imports always last
- ✅ Blank line between import groups
- ✅ No blank lines within same group
- ✅ Alphabetical order within each group

